  <scopecontent id="aspace_4ca625be62f9cfc0a4740d04fba20b78">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Records include correspondence, meeting minutes, scrapbooks, membership lists, notes pertaining to induction ceremonies, printed and mimeographed material, photographs, awards, and other items pertaining to Sigma Gamma Rho.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_34f00b4e6ca2fa3564d286d4a2a51876">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Sigma Gamma Rho, Lambda Omicron chapter records, #37-4-3712. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <accessrestrict audience="internal" id="aspace_54aaeb6d2b4af0042809927f99f40301">
    <head>Access Restrictions:</head>
<p>Access to Box 2 restricted to members of the Lambda Omicron members of Sigma Gamma Rho Sorority with current ID (List of chapter members in the accession folder.)</p>  </accessrestrict>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_c48f4c02be532cd81fd5d85a2d7002dd">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>The Lambda Omicron chapter of Sigma Gamma Rho was established at Cornell University in 1990.</p>  </bioghist>
